36#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
37#include <config.h>
38#endif
39
40#include <stdio.h>
41#include <string.h>
42
43#ifdef KRB5
44extern const char *heimdal_version;
45#endif
46#include <version.h>
47
48int
49main(int argc, char **argv)
50{
51 FILE *f;
52 if(argc != 2)
53 return 1;
54 if (strcmp(argv[1], "--version") == 0) {
55 printf("some version");
56 return 0;
57 }
58 f = fopen(argv[1], "w");
59 if(f == NULL)
60 return 1;
61 fprintf(f, "#define VERSIONLIST \"");
62#ifdef KRB5
63 fprintf(f, "%s", heimdal_version);
64#endif
65 fprintf(f, "\"\n");
66 fclose(f);
67 return 0;
68}
